<p>Well, we have a portfolio page, but you can see this is now very manual to maintain. I don‚Äôt know about you, but I don‚Äôt want to sit and type in all that data for every book. Ideally we want to be able to have just one block of <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;li&gt;...&lt;/li&gt;</code> code, and programmatically insert the data in to it, getting the code to repeat itself once for each book. That‚Äôs what we‚Äôll do next.</p>

<h2 id="what-youve-learned">What you‚Äôve learned</h2>

<ul>
  <li>We can add HTML to a page</li>
  <li>But duplicating it is manual and requires too much maintenance</li>
</ul>
